      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"close the book\"... yeah, that's exactly what it feels like. like i'm just staring at the last page and looking for the exit. it's weird, because everyone else is so obsessed with the next destination, but all i can think about is how much better it would be to just... sign off. to finally reach the final station and not have to worry about the next ticket. do you think there's actually anything beautiful about just letting it all go?",
